{"tid":200291,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[政界倫敦金] 熱狗賺錢方程式大揭秘","createTime":"2017-04-13T22:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T06:54:14.000Z","uid":28938,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"359af1d0d8f9b1f8cb3cba6f9caa97aa007edb60","tid":200291,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T22:39:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>步驟1：理念期</strong><br />\n以「勇武」為主題，吸納懷有理想的年青人與學生加入。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>步驟2：培養期</strong><br />\n以各種活動主題，說服成員掏腰包課金贊助，並加強他們對組織的歸屬感。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>步驟3：行動期</strong><br />\n舉辦各種街頭活動，鼓勵年青人前線抗爭並與警員衝突，成功令他們惹上官非。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>步驟4：收成期</strong><br />\n以「為義士打官司」為名籌款，最終只尋找法庭當值律師協助，巨款袋袋平安。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>步驟5：旅遊期</strong><br />\n黃氏夫婦善用課金籌款去各地旅行，食清淡d，放空腦袋，尋找課金籌款idea。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>步驟6：排便期</strong><br />\n黃氏夫婦細心分析對組織再沒利用價值的成員，透過組織輿論將他們逐出，再重新步驟1，為組織吸納優質成員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s0gW194.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs0gW194.jpg&h=cda24041&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca3cd0f882db76e1fe80b92eb22cd2941e8027c7","tid":200291,"uid":72990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T22:55:35.000Z","msg":"五毛呀你 你拎高登仔最鐘意既熱血黎講<br />\n死無葬身之地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e03f19295b9f227fb18928f702c05333a5888c","tid":200291,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T23:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五毛呀你 你拎高登仔最鐘意既熱血黎講<br />\n死無葬身之地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我相信每個人都有獨立思考既能力，係人係鬼點會睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a28149c5fddd4e4a3e0d545533e9a15f9f27ff","tid":200291,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T23:02:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"113cfca1be28f877827a7d45b9af0f5c768688f8","tid":200291,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13